title: Count of windows RDP Sessions
agents: windows
catalog: os/kernel
license: Proprietary
distribution: MIS Monitoring Desk
description:
  This check uses qwinsta.exe to determine the numer of RDP session on a machine. 
  It checks the total number of sessions, but reports as perfdata the counters by
  session state (https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/cc754930%28v=ws.11%29.aspx#BKMK_SST)

item:
 None

perfdata:
  total sessions counter and the same split by session state

inventory:
 This check supports inventory.
